The article is a transcript of remarks made by President Trump and various political leaders in the Oval Office. The leaders express their desire to come to an agreement on funding the government, supporting soldiers, and helping average citizens. They also discuss bipartisan issues such as addressing the opioid crisis, helping veterans, and children's health insurance. The Vice President expresses confidence in achieving results before Christmas, while Secretary Mattis emphasizes the importance of protecting the Constitution and bipartisan support.